replies.bodyText:
In either case, KubernetesCloudTest#testInstanceCap fails because concurrency limit checking is skipped when the pod template has a limit but the overall cloud is unlimited.
FTR Pod templates are using Integer.MAX_VALUE to mean unlimited:



      kubernetes-plugin/src/main/java/org/csanchez/jenkins/plugins/kubernetes/PodTemplate.java


