           public void setInstanceCap(int instanceCap) { 




               if (instanceCap < 0) { 




                   this.instanceCap = Integer.MAX_VALUE; 




               } else { 




                   this.instanceCap = instanceCap; 




               } 




           } 





I'll toy around with it some more until tests pass.

